        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Upon being mixed and injected into the bloodstream, this powder of the crimson orchid quickly assaults the brain and nerves, disrupting the victim's ability to piece together coherent thoughts and spells.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">T</span> Interact (Injury)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> DC 32 Fortitude</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"mental\" data-formula=\"2d6\" title=\"mental\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 2d6</a> mental damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied} 2 (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"mental\" data-formula=\"3d6\" title=\"mental\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 3d6</a> mental damage and stupefied 3 (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"mental\" data-formula=\"4d6\" title=\"mental\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 4d6</a> mental damage and stupefied 4 (1 round)</p>"
